author: @huckleberry582
text: Just a quick thought about getting your IP address. I have an app on my android called Fing. It will scan your network and list anything that is connected to your wireless network. Once you run it, you can rename each thing that is accessing and it remembers those names. It is free and it has come in handy and is worth a try if you need to check IP addresses periodically.
